$$$LIST.text:
FROM 'TSAZF.CBT.ALZ.DYNAMIC.USERMODS'
    $$APP    - SMP/E APPLY JOB for working with USERMODs
    $$REC    - SMP/E RECEIVE JOB for working with USERMODs
    $$REJ    - SMP/E REJECT JOB for working with USERMODs
    $$RES    - SMP/E RESTORE/REJECT JOB for working with USERMODs

    #ISPF01  - USERMOD to support ISPF PROFILE Sharing in RMF
    #ISPF02  - USERMOD to support ISPF PROFILE Sharing in SDSF
    #ISPF03  - USERMOD to support ISPF PROFILE Sharing in HCD

    #ISPF04  - ISPCCONF option 6 created USERMOD (Place Holder)

    #ISPF05  - USERMOD to make IBM ISPF ONLY Macro available

    #TSO001  - Ed Jaffe's TSO SUB=MSTR USERMOD (Place Holder). Download
               from Phoenix Software's website & fit to your level of
               TSO. ftp://phoenixsoftware.com/pub/demo/tsomods.xmi

#ISPF01.text:
++USERMOD(#ISPF01) REWORK(yyyyjjj)  /*
   ISPF CList, EXEC, & Panel Changes to fully support ISPF SHARED
   Profiles in IBM Base Software. This includes:
     - RMF  (Support Image Specific RMF MON 3 Datasets)

   1. Copy AERBCLS(ERBRMF3X)
   2. Do a "F 'SET TABLSUF ='
   3. Replace with the following

*/ .
++VER(Z038) FMID(HRM77??) /* PRE(U??????) */ .
++CLIST(ERBRMF3X) SYSLIB(SERBCLS)  DISTLIB(AERBCLS)     .
 /*-------------------- ISPF SHRPROF Support ------------------------*/
 /*     Replace "SET TABLSUF = &STR(ISPTABLE)" with Following        */
 /*-------------------- ---------------------------------------------*/
 SET TABLSUF = &STR(ISPTABLE).SYS&STR(&SYSSMFID) /* For ISPF SHRPROF */
 /*-------------------- ISPF SHRPROF Support ------------------------*/

#ISPF02.text:
++USERMOD(#ISPF02) REWORK(yyyyjjj)  /*

   ISPF CList, EXEC, & Panel Changes to fully support ISPF SHARED
   Profiles in IBM Base Software. This includes:
     - SDSF (Support Image Specific Consoles in a Shared Environment)

   1. Copy AISFPLIB(ISFPCU41)
   2. Do a "F ')PROC' 1"
   3. Add the following before )PROC Section (at end of )INIT section)

*/ .
++VER(Z038) FMID(HQX77??) /* PRE(U??????) */ .
++PNL(ISFPCU41) SYSLIB(SISFPLIB)  DISTLIB(AISFPLIB)     .
   /*   At the Very END of )INIT Section, before )PROC Section   */
   /*        Added for ISPF SHRPROF Support                      */
*REXX(*,FIRST,ISFCMD)
  IF FIRST = "" THEN DO
     FIRST = "TRUE"
     ISFCMD = "SET CONSOLE" STRIP(LEFT(USERID(),6))MVSVAR("SYSCLONE")
    END
   ELSE FIRST = "FALSE"
*ENDREXX
 IF (&FIRST = TRUE) .RESP = ENTER
     /*        Added for ISPF SHRPROF Support                      */

#ISPF03.text:
++USERMOD(#ISPF03) REWORK(yyyyjjj)  /*

   ISPF CList, EXEC, & Panel Changes to fully support ISPF SHARED
   Profiles in IBM Base Software. This includes:
     - HCD  (Support Image Specific HCD Datasets)

   1. Copy ACBDCLST(CBDCHCD)
   2. Do a "C '&PFX = &SYSUID' '&PFX = &SYSUID..&SYSSMFID' ALL"

*/ .
++VER(Z038) FMID(HCS77??) /* PRE(U??????) */ .
++CLIST(CBDCHCD) SYSLIB(SCBDCLST) DISTLIB(ACBDCLST)    .
 /************ Updated for ISPF SHRPROF Support *************/
 SELECT
    WHEN (&NOPREF  = NO)      SET &PFX = &SYSUID..&SYSSMFID
    WHEN (&SYSPREF = &SYSUID) SET &PFX = &SYSUID..&SYSSMFID
    WHEN (&SYSPREF = &STR() ) SET &PFX = &SYSUID..&SYSSMFID
    OTHERWISE                 SET &PFX = &SYSPREF..&SYSUID..&SYSSMFID
 /************ Updated for ISPF SHRPROF Support *************/

#ISPF04.text: /* Created via ISPF ISPCCONF configuration utility option 6 */

#ISPF05.text:
++USERMOD(#ISPF05)  REWORK(yyyyjjj) /*

  Define IBM's ISPF Macro %ONLY using ISRONLY sample

*/.
++VER(Z038) FMID(HIF7P??)  /* PRE(U??????) */ .
++EXEC(ISRONLY) ALIAS(ONLY)     DISTLIB(AISPEXEC)
                TXLIB(SISPSAMP)  SYSLIB(SISPEXEC) .
